					<div id="mw-content-text" class="mw-body-content"><div class="mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output" lang="en" dir="ltr"><div class="shortdescription nomobile noexcerpt noprint searchaux" style="display:none">British philosopher and social and political theorist (1909–1997)</div>
<div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable">This article is about the 20th-century philosopher. For the 18th-century rabbi, see <a href="/wiki/Isaiah_Berlin_(rabbi)" title="Isaiah Berlin (rabbi)">Isaiah Berlin (rabbi)</a>.</div>
<p class="mw-empty-elt">

</p>
