<li><i>The Proper Study of Mankind: An Anthology of Essays</i> (edited by Henry Hardy and Roger Hausheer) [a one-volume selection from the whole of Berlin's work], Chatto &amp; Windus, 1997. 2nd ed., Vintage, 2013. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-0099582762" title="Special:BookSources/978-0099582762">978-0099582762</a>.</li>
